OL,3,CTracking down the last veterans of D-
OL,4,CDay to tell their stories
OL,6,FITV News Meridian has interviewed more
OL,7,Fthan 80 veterans up and down the
OL,8,Fcountry as part of our coverage of the
OL,9,F80th anniversary of D-Day.
OL,11,FLed by our reporter Derek Johnson, he
OL,12,Fand camera operator Siobhan Hart,
OL,13,Fworked tirelessly to capture the
OL,14,Fstories of those involved in , to
OL,15,Fensure they are never forgotten. You
OL,16,Fcan find all of them .
OL,18,FFor 15 years, Derek and Shiv have been
OL,19,Ftravelling to the beaches, memorials
OL,20,Fand cemeteries of Normandy for ITV
OL,21,FNews Meridian.
