OL,3,CTracking down the last veterans of D-
OL,4,CDay to tell their stories
OL,6,FBoth have covered events commemorating
OL,7,FD-Day, the Allied invasion of occupied
OL,8,FEurope in 1944 in which 156,000 troops
OL,9,Fcrossed the English Channel by air and
OL,10,Fsea in a single day and landed in
OL,11,FFrance.
OL,13,FTo mark 80 years, Shiv wanted to go
OL,14,Ffurther than ITV News Meridian has
OL,15,Fever gone before, and, with the help
OL,16,Fof colleagues Kate Taylor and Sandor
OL,17,FTaylor, tracked down more than 80
OL,18,Fveterans, some of whom had never
OL,19,Fbefore told their stories.
