OL,4,CDay to tell their stories
OL,6,FThe idea was to ensure that their
OL,7,Fstories would be told 'in full', not
OL,8,Fcut down to fit into a 30-minute
OL,9,Fprogramme.
OL,11,FThis coincided with the launch of
OL,12,FITV's streaming platform, , which
OL,13,Fallows regional news teams to publish
OL,14,Flong-form, bespoke journalism, making
OL,15,Fit all possible.
