OL,3,CTracking down the last veterans of D-
OL,4,CDay to tell their stories
OL,6,FThey are available on a dedicated ,
OL,7,Fwhere they will remain long after that
OL,8,Fliving link disappears.
OL,10,FIt is not military history. Not a
OL,11,Fstory about ranks and regiments,
OL,12,Ftactics, strategy and weaponry.
OL,14,FIt is the testimony of people who
OL,15,Flived through extraordinary times, did
OL,16,Ftheir duty, and somehow came out the
OL,17,Fother side.
